page.title: 10PITTINGTON HILL (cont.)
page.content:
MAY-dandelion, daisy, cowslip, violet, white dead nettle, red dead nettle, coltsfoot, gorse, celandine, buqle, two types of chickweed, birds eye, germander speedwell, wild strawberry, plantain, sorrel, hog weed, shepherds purse, hawthorn, early purple orchid.
JUNE-germander speedwell, shepherds purse, chickweed, plantain, hogweed, birds foot trefoil, sorrel, may blossom, kidney vetch, milkwort, buttercup, daisy, cowslip, clover, rock rose, great bernet, orchid, gorse, Herb Robert, lady's bedstraw, ragwort.
